FROM [Users] AS [u]
LEFT JOIN [Blogs] AS [b] ON [u].[UserId] = [b].[UserId]

LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [u].[UserId] = [p].[UserId]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]

ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

2024-11-21 02:28:57.683 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[EndTime], [t].[StartTime], [t].[ProductId], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[StartingPrice], [c].[CategoryName]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[EndTime], [a].[ProductId], [a].[StartTime]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()
    ORDER BY [a].[ProductId]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [t].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT TOP(1) [a].[EndTime], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Bids] AS [b]
    WHERE [a].[AuctionId] = [b].[AuctionId]) AS [TotalBids], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[StartingPrice], [p].[Country], [p].[Brand], [p].[Quantity], [p].[Stock], [p].[Views], [p].[CreatedAt], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing' AND [a].[AuctionId] = @__auctionId_0 AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[EndTime], [t].[StartTime], [t].[ProductId], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[StartingPrice], [c].[CategoryName]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[EndTime], [t].[StartTime], [t].[ProductId], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[StartingPrice], [c].[CategoryName]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

    SELECT [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[EndTime], [a].[StartTime], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[CategoryId] = @__categoryId_0 AND [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[CategoryId]

    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()
    ORDER BY [a].[ProductId]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [t].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[CategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[ProductId]

SELECT TOP(1) [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[EndTime], [t].[StartTime], [t].[ProductId], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[StartingPrice], [c].[CategoryName]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[EndTime], [a].[ProductId], [a].[StartTime]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()
    ORDER BY [a].[ProductId]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

ORDER BY [t].[ProductId]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]

    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]

ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[EndTime], [t].[StartTime], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], [c].[CategoryName]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[EndTime], [a].[StartTime], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[CategoryId] = @__categoryId_0 AND [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY

    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [a].[AuctionId], COALESCE([p].[ProductName], N'Unknown Product'), [a].[CurrentHighestBid], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [u].[UserId], [u].[Username], [u].[Email]

INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]

    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedAt], [u].[Email], [u].[Gender], [u].[ImageUrl], [u].[IsAdmin], [u].[IsDeleted], [u].[Password], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[PasswordSalt], [u].[UpdatedAt], [u].[Username], [u].[otp], [b].[BlogId], [b].[ApprovalStatus], [b].[Content], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[PublishedAt], [b].[Title], [b].[UserId], [b].[ViewCount], [b0].[BidId], [b0].[AuctionId], [b0].[BidAmount], [b0].[BidTime], [b0].[UserId], [p].[PaymentId], [p].[AuctionId], [p].[IsNotificationSent], [p].[PaymentAmount], [p].[PaymentDate], [p].[PaymentDueDate], [p].[PaymentLink], [p].[PaymentStatus], [p].[UserId]
FROM [Users] AS [u]
LEFT JOIN [Blogs] AS [b] ON [u].[UserId] = [b].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b0] ON [u].[UserId] = [b0].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN [Payments] AS [p] ON [u].[UserId] = [p].[UserId]
WHERE [u].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
ORDER BY [u].[UserId], [b].[BlogId], [b0].[BidId]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]

ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[EndTime], [t].[StartTime], [t].[ProductId], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[StartingPrice], [c].[CategoryName]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[EndTime], [a].[ProductId], [a].[StartTime]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()
    ORDER BY [a].[ProductId]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [t].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[CategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[ProductId]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]
2024-11-21 11:58:04.673 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (12ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(1) [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]

    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]
